{
  "icon": "minecraft:writable_book",
  "title": "Part IV: How Elixir Quality Works",
  "contents": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "When you collect an elixir, it receives a quality rating based on the final manifested strength of its essences. This is determined by the resulting [color=#EC8FFF]weight[/color] after all modifiers have been applied."
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "columns": [
        {
          "header": "Weight",
          "weight": 2.0
        },
        {
          "header": "Quality",
          "weight": 3.0
        },
        {
          "header": "Rarity",
          "weight": 3.0
        }
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "0-29",
          "Pale",
          "[color=#FFFFFF]Common[/color]"
        ],
        [
          "30-39",
          "Cloudy",
          "[color=#FFFFFF]Common[/color]"
        ],
        [
          "40-49",
          "Weak",
          "[color=#FFFFFF]Common[/color]"
        ],
        [
          "50-59",
          "Minor",
          "[color=#FFFFFF]Common[/color]"
        ],
        [
          "60-69",
          "Moderate",
          "[color=#FFFFFF]Common[/color]"
        ],
        [
          "70-79",
          "Grand",
          "[color=#FFFFFF]Common[/color]"
        ],
        [
          "80-89",
          "Intense",
          "[color=#FFFF55]Uncommon[/color]"
        ],
        [
          "90-99",
          "Supreme",
          "[color=#55FFFF]Rare[/color]"
        ],
        [
          "100",
          "Legendary",
          "[color=#FF5FFF]Epic[/color]"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blank"
    },
    {
      "type": "subheader",
      "text": "Manifestation"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "[color=#EC8FFF]Manifestation[/color] measures how many different ingredients contribute the same essence. It is calculated separately for each essence. Shared contributions reinforce manifestation, while isolated essences remain weak."
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "columns": [
        {
          "header": "Tier",
          "content_color": "#FFEC8FFF",
          "weight": 2.0
        },
        {
          "header": "Distinct Sources",
          "weight": 2.0
        },
        {
          "header": "Multiplier",
          "weight": 2.0
        }
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "Dominant",
          "3",
          "×1.2"
        ],
        [
          "Primary",
          "2",
          "×1.0"
        ],
        [
          "Trace",
          "1",
          "×0.2"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blank"
    },
    {
      "type": "subheader",
      "text": "Diversity"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "[color=#EC8FFF]Diversity[/color] measures ingredient repetition across the entire brew. Unlike Manifestation, it does not examine essences individually. Repeating ingredients globally reduces the strength of all outcomes."
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "columns": [
        {
          "header": "Tier",
          "content_color": "#FFEC8FFF",
          "weight": 2.0
        },
        {
          "header": "Ingredient Pattern",
          "weight": 3.0
        },
        {
          "header": "Multiplier",
          "weight": 2.0
        }
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "Distinct",
          "3 different ingredients",
          "×1.0"
        ],
        [
          "Repeated",
          "2 identical, 1 different",
          "×0.6"
        ],
        [
          "Uniform",
          "3 identical ingredients",
          "×0.2"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blank"
    },
    {
      "type": "subheader",
      "text": "Concordance"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "[color=#EC8FFF]Concordance[/color] reflects how closely the brew aligns with the [color=#8fe1ff]Inhibitor[/color]'s Aspect. It is applied globally as a final multiplier to all manifested essences."
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "columns": [
        {
          "header": "Tier",
          "content_color": "#FFEC8FFF",
          "weight": 2.0
        },
        {
          "header": "Aspect Alignment",
          "weight": 3.0
        },
        {
          "header": "Multiplier",
          "weight": 2.0
        }
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "Perfect",
          "Full alignment",
          "×1.4"
        ],
        [
          "Partial",
          "Some alignment",
          "×1.2"
        ],
        [
          "None",
          "No alignment",
          "×1.0"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blank"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The strongest elixirs emerge when these systems reinforce one another: shared essences create strong [color=#EC8FFF]Manifestation[/color], varied ingredients preserve [color=#EC8FFF]Diversity[/color], and aligned Aspects maximize [color=#EC8FFF]Concordance[/color]."
    }
  ]
}